    ns2:isAbout <http://example.org/req/622#TextAlwaysEnergized> .

<http://example.org/req/622#EV_4_4_1_Spec> a <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000001>,
        <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000002>,
        <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000031>,
