<http://example.org/req/622#DS_GLVSystem> a <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000001>,
        <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000002>,
        <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000031>,
        owl:NamedIndividual,
